title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast November 6: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Stocks gained for a fifth straight week after the Federal Reserve offered no surprises in its policy announcement and companies reported quarterly earnings that mostly beat estimates.
